<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Dama Korea privacy policy."><article class="article-shell legal-page"><h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p>Last updated: July 15, 2026</p><p>Dama Korea is committed to collecting as little personal information as practical. This policy explains what may be processed when you use damaheritage.com.</p><h2>Information you provide</h2><p>If you contact us by email, we receive your email address and the information you choose to include. Do not send identity documents or sensitive financial information. We use correspondence to respond, investigate corrections and operate the site.</p><h2>Analytics, cookies and advertising</h2><p>The site may use analytics and Google AdSense. These services may process device information, approximate location, browser data and interactions, and may use cookies or similar technologies subject to consent requirements in your region. Google explains how it uses information from sites that use its services in its published privacy documentation.</p><h2>Legal basis and choices</h2><p>Where applicable, processing may rely on consent, legitimate interests in operating and securing the site, or legal obligations. Browser controls and any consent interface offered on the site can be used to manage optional cookies.</p><h2>Retention and sharing</h2><p>Correspondence is kept only as long as reasonably needed for the purpose it was sent or legal obligations. Information is not sold. Service providers may process limited data to host, secure, measure or monetize the site.</p><h2>Contact</h2><p>Privacy questions can be sent to <a href="mailto:support@damaheritage.com?subject=Privacy">support@damaheritage.com</a>.</p></article></BaseLayout>
